728293f-a.folder: Altamount Street & Beacon Avenue, Staten Island, NY
728293f-a.text:
(1)
Altamount Street, west side, between Beacon Avenue and Kildare Street, showing the Eew Dorp Lighthouse. The beacon
is about 150 feet back of the street.
